author: Ron Dicker
title: Cate Blanchett Performing With Drag Queens Is All You Need Right Now
text:
02/22/2017 09:41 am ET Cate Blanchett Performing With Drag Queens Is All You Need Right Now The Oscar winner vamped it up for a cause at the iconic Stonewall Inn gay bar. — ariane (@helenasbby) February 21, 2017 
Cate Blanchett electrified a drag show at New York City’s Stonewall Inn Monday night by lip-synching “You Don’t Own Me.” Other performers then backed up the actress for the fab finish. 
As you can see in the video below, the two-time Oscar winner wasn’t about to be upstaged.
